Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description":"Válvula check de acero bridada 10.5 kgs. De 152 mm. (6\" 150 lbs.), astm a216 gr.wcb mca walworth fig.5341f trim 8"
}

### Products overview
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/overview

### Family distribution
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/family-distribution?top=15

### Prefix patterns
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/prefix-patterns?top=20

### First word analysis
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/first-word-analysis?top=200

### First word normalization report
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/first-word-normalization-report?topReview=50

### Category candidates
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/category-candidates

### Category conflicts
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/category-conflicts?limit=100

### Normalization preview
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/normalization-preview?limit=20&offset=0

### Normalization preview by bucket
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/normalization-preview?limit=200&offset=0&categoryBucket=TUBO_ACERO

### Normalized batch
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/normalized-batch?limit=20&offset=0

### Normalized batch by bucket
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/normalized-batch?limit=20&offset=0&categoryBucket=TUBO_PLASTICO

### Missing EAN batch
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/missing-ean-batch?limit=20&offset=0

### Missing EAN batch by bucket
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/missing-ean-batch?limit=20&offset=0&categoryBucket=TUBO_ACERO

### Missing EAN stored in Neon
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/missing-ean-stored?limit=20&offset=0

### Sync normalized batch to Neon
POST http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/sync-normalized-batch?limit=20&offset=0

### Sync normalized batch to Neon by bucket

POST http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/sync-normalized-batch?limit=20&offset=0&categoryBucket=VALVULA

### Sync all normalized products
POST http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/sync-normalized-all?limit=200&startOffset=0

### Sync all normalized products by bucket
POST http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/sync-normalized-all?limit=200&startOffset=0&categoryBucket=TUBO_ACERO
